text: Urspringen is a community in the Main-Spessart district in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (Administrative Community) of Marktheidenfeld. == Geography == === Location === Urspringen is in the Würzburg Region. The community has only the Gemarkung (traditional rural cadastral area) of Urspringen. == References == == Other websites == * Community’s official webpage Category:Main-Spessart
title: Urspringen
